column3: Near beaver cabin on edge of access route from gateway
Canopy tree.  It was recorded as T x europaea 1/2/2019 but in winter with no fresh leaves so T.cordata more likely to be correct.
Canopy significantly higher than 1/2/2019 (5%) as the survey location is near the edge
Up to 4 in ruts as quadrat fell on track
On 1/2/2019 (85%) and 21/6/19 (80%) quadrat further from track and canopy cover was higher
On damp edge of the central drainage ditch on former arable
up to 5 as next to open water of central drainage channel.  Open water 30% of quadrat.
